<h2 style="font-size:100%; font-weight:bold; border: none; margin: 0; padding:0; padding-bottom:.1em; color:#8B0000;"><span class="mw-headline" id="Did_You_Know.3F">Did You Know?</span></h2>
</div>
<div style="border: 1px solid #ed9121; border-top-width: 1px; vertical-align: top;background: #ffec8b;opacity: 1; color: black; text-align: left; margin: 0 0 10px; padding: 1em;padding-top: .3em;">
<ul>
<li><a href="Ashvagosha" title="Ashvagosha" class="mw-redirect">Ashvagosha</a>, the first <a href="Sanskrit" title="Sanskrit">Sanskrit</a> dramatist, was advisor to the <a href="Buddhist" title="Buddhist" class="mw-redirect">Buddhist</a> king, <a href="Kanishka" title="Kanishka">Kanishka</a>.</li>
<li><a href="Zen" title="Zen">Zen</a> was brought to <a href="Japanese_Buddhism" title="Japanese Buddhism" class="mw-redirect">Japan</a> in the late 12th century, by the monk <a href="Eisai" title="Eisai">Eisai</a>.</li>
</ul>
<div class="noprint" style="text-align:right; margin:0.3em 0.2em 0.2em 0.3em; padding:0.3em 0.2em 0.2em 0.3em;"></div>
<div style="clear:both;"></div>
</div>
